{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839403407,"sessionID":"ses_287bcb93dffe74sqV2FOvjBYfr","part":{"id":"prt_d7846da13001wvDvpYdLY0VXom","messageID":"msg_d7846bd12001EMAPfRSNd3KqU7","sessionID":"ses_287bcb93dffe74sqV2FOvjBYfr","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_8570603051744c679b005565","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-015/design.md`, `changes/AR-015/proposal.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. TODO\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 TODO\n12: \n13: **Verification:** TODO\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## T2. TODO\n18: \n19: - [ ] 2.1 TODO\n20: \n21: **Verification:** TODO\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## T3. TODO\n26: \n27: - [ ] 3.1 TODO\n28: \n29: **Verification:** TODO\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ## Task Dependencies\n34: \n35: ```\n36: T1 ──→ T2 ──→ T3\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Acceptance Criteria\n40: \n41: | # | Criterion | Command |\n42: |---|-----------|---------|\n43: | AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/picod/...` |\n44: | AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` |\n45: | AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` |\n46: | AC4 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` |\n\n(End of file - total 46 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/picod\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-015/design.md`, `changes/AR-015/proposal.md`\n\n## T1. TODO\n\n- [ ] 1.1 TODO\n\n**Verification:** TODO\n\n---\n\n## T2. TODO\n\n- [ ] 2.1 TODO\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":